@startuml
title Sequence 05 - Evaluasi Kecocokan Profil, CV, dan Lowongan
autonumber
participant "Celery Worker" as Worker
participant "AI Matching Service" as AI
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "LLM Provider" as LLM

Worker -> AI: match_job_skills(application_id)
AI -> DB: Ambil application, student skills, vacancy skills
DB --> AI: Data profil dan kebutuhan lowongan
AI -> AI: Hitung overlap skill dan skor awal
alt LLM tersedia
  AI -> LLM: Minta reasoning kecocokan
  LLM --> AI: Reasoning/rekomendasi
else LLM tidak tersedia
  AI -> AI: Gunakan fallback deterministic score
end
AI -> DB: Simpan/return hasil match untuk FE
DB --> AI: Commit OK
AI --> Worker: Task selesai
@enduml
